Program: Great Lives
Title: David Lloyd George
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0076f9j
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 6 Feb 2015
Athlete Tanni Grey-Thompson chooses her Welsh compatriot, politician David Lloyd George. With Humphrey Carpenter. The biographical series in which a distinguished guest chooses someone who's inspired their life. Will their hero stand up to intensive scrutiny and merit the description of having led a great life? From 2003. Show less